{"tid":333393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲對拍拖無咩憧憬","createTime":"2017-07-23T18:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T09:26:13.000Z","uid":76614,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a05f21fc5ea3db086edfb3d971c72b675b6ffef","tid":333393,"uid":76614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:30:05.000Z","msg":"唔好插我因爲無另一半先咁講<br />\n或是係我既一啲經歷令我對拍拖無咩信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又見身邊朋友好多拍拖既 另一半又會暪住去蒲去玩<br />\n 熱戀期左一年之後 去到簡簡單單既平淡期 捱到兩三年既又嫌悶又想要自由 看似穩定拍左四五年 總有一方去搞搞陣 好似不停循環 每段關係都係大致係咁 忍到就白頭到老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  拍拖又要交代呢樣個樣 諗諗下搞到對拍拖無晒憧憬 可能陰影太大又眼見身邊既人都唔是太好"},{"pid":"3adeae271ac7086866c43eab22df8d8191ba1dc7","tid":333393,"uid":77999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:47:30.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e4d2c68ed800e4b575f8177cea475f09b075f5","tid":333393,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:52:19.000Z","msg":"對任何野都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順其自然吧啦憧乜撚"},{"pid":"6928c0c0f4cff913f519c9db55ad5276d81d8ded","tid":333393,"uid":76614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T23:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對任何野都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順其自然吧啦憧乜撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係應該對任何野都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sad but true"},{"pid":"5f874381d9c1eacebf517e27323d67f999edd64a","tid":333393,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T00:00:10.000Z","msg":"愛情就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都覺得好攰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾多浪漫 又轟烈既愛情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大部分正如你所講  去到兩三年開始淡 頂唔到就換"},{"pid":"b2cb495d7e8455ffdc71e6e56115fb669b7a20fb","tid":333393,"uid":76614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor